E_SUIS_INDISPONIBLE_FR":"I'm unavailable","july":"July","june":"June","LA_REGLE":"The rule","LEGAL_INFORMATION_GDPR":"The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) will be applicable from May 25th, 2018.\n \nIn order to enable us to activate the consent request for your visitors, we must collect the legal information that will be displayed to your visitors. For this, please complete the following information:\n\n1\u00b0) What is your website url?\n\n2\u00b0) If you know them, what are your iAdvize CID / SID?\n\n3\u00b0) Provide your \u201cidentity and contact details of the data controller\u201d (mandatory)\nExample: Company name, detailed address, phone, email\n\n4\u00b0) Provide your \u201ccontact details of the Data Protection Officer\u201d (optional)\nExample: Name & email address\n\n5\u00b0) Review the following template of the \u201cPurposes of processing of the personal data and the legal basis for it\u201d (mandatory)\nWe collect and process your data because you gave us your express consent\nPurpose: We collect and keep records of chats so we can provide you the best possible support and enhance our products and services\n\n6\u00b0) Provide your \u201cRecipients of the personal data\u201d (mandatory)\n\n7\u00b0) Review the following template of the \u201cInformation on any cross-border data transfers outside the EEA\u201d (mandatory)\nFor Chat: your data will be hosted by the European Union\nFor Call/Video/text messages: EU and US (protected by Privacy Shield and standard contractual clauses)\n\n8\u00b0) Review the following template for \u201cYour rights\u201d (mandatory)\nUnconditional rights\nAt any time, you may:\n\n- Rectify your personal data\n- Obtain a copy of such personal data\n\nConditional rights\nAs the case may be, you may :\n\n- Withdraw your consent where one of our use is based hereupon\n- Request the transfer to anyone of data we hold on the basis of your consent\n- Request that we keep your data without using it in case of inaccuracy, unlawfulness, while we examine your refusal that we use your data or should you need it before courts\n- Request deletion in case data is unnecessary or where you have withdrawn consent\n\nFinally, you may introduce a claim with the data protection authority of your country.\n\n9\u00b0) Do you have other legal information to display to your visitors? (optional)\n\nWe thank you in advance for your cooperation!","livechat.callbox.close.title":"Close dialog","livechat.callbox.phoneNumber.label":"Enter your phone number.","livechat.chatbox.conversation.satisfactionMessage":"Your satisfaction is at the heart of our concerns. Please take a few seconds to evaluate the quality of this exchange. \ud83d\ude42","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.contactDataController":"Identity and contact details of the data controller","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.contactDataProtectionOfficer":"Contact details of the Data Protection Officer","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.dataTransfers":"Information on any cross-border data transfers outside the EEA \ud83c\uddea\ud83c\uddfa.","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.explanation":"We need this information in order to interact with our customers:\n- We save the conversation for a period of 3 years\n- We allow our agents to see your browsing in real-time on our website (not saved)\n- We allow our agents to preview your messages (not saved)","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.explanations":"We need this information in order to interact with our customers:\n- We save the conversation for a period of {DURATION}\n- We allow our agents to see your browsing in real-time on our website (not saved)\n- We allow our agents to preview your messages (not saved)","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.explanations.duration.days":"{DURATION} days","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.explanations.duration.years":"{DURATION} years","livechat.conversations.consent.legal.otherInformation":"Other information","livechat.conversations.consent.legal